you're right for her.

264
00:11:54,655 --> 00:11:57,624
I give you
one simple thing to do--

265
00:11:57,626 --> 00:12:00,761
contact a complete stranger and
make her fall in love with me--

266
00:12:00,763 --> 00:12:02,562
and you blow it!

267
00:12:02,564 --> 00:12:05,799
I told her
what a good guy you are, but

268
00:12:05,801 --> 00:12:07,868
she thought it
was a bad sign

269
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:09,870
