to her yourself.

270
00:12:09,872 --> 00:12:13,807
She thought it made you seem
too shy and passive.

271
00:12:13,809 --> 00:12:15,675
I'm not too shy and passive.

272
00:12:15,677 --> 00:12:18,311
You write her back
and tell her I said that.

273
00:12:18,313 --> 00:12:21,381
You know,
when you have a second.

274
00:12:21,383 --> 00:12:24,885
Look, I'll see if I can change
her mind tomorrow night.

275
00:12:24,887 --> 00:12:26,520
What's happening tomorrow night?

276
00:12:26,522 --> 00:12:28,054
