277
00:12:28,056 --> 00:12:29,489
What?!

278
00:12:29,491 --> 00:12:31,558
Well, we just... we e-mailed
back and forth a bit,

279
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,059
and we kind of
hit it off.

280
00:12:33,061 --> 00:12:35,343
I find a girl I like,
and you're stealing her?!

281
00:12:35,368 --> 00:12:35,963
No.

282
00:12:35,964 --> 00:12:37,831
We just ended up
having a lot in common.

283
00:12:37,833 --> 00:12:39,933
We went to Harvard,
we like Chaucer,

284
00:12:39,935 --> 00:12:42,669
we're both hardcore
into quilting.

285
00:12:45,373 --> 00:12:47,407
Your words fall like acid rain

286
00:12:47,409 --> 00:12:49,643
on the wounded petals
of my heart.

287
00:12:51,913 --> 00:12:53,547
That's Sheldon.

288
00:12:53,549 --> 00:12:55,515
He says he'll be down
in a minute.

289
00:12:55,517 --> 00:12:57,517
What are you doing?

290
00:12:57,519 --> 00:13:00,153
Oh, he's not coming out
until he sees proof

291
00:13:00,155 --> 00:13:02,722
you don't have an air freshener
in your car.

292
00:13:03,758 --> 00:13:06,726
This is gonna be a long weekend
for you.

293
00:13:06,728 --> 00:13:09,396
You're the reason I'm doing it!
I said

294
00:13:09,398 --> 00:13:10,764
to stop insulting each other.

295
00:13:10,766 --> 00:13:13,867
