scared of turbulence!

348
00:15:46,989 --> 00:15:48,888
I'm gonna need
that bag back.

349
00:15:52,693 --> 00:15:54,194
You sure you want
to do this?

350
00:15:54,196 --> 00:15:56,629
Yeah. Why wouldn't I want
