351
00:15:56,631 --> 00:15:58,098
It'll be fun to see everyone.

352
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:00,066
I haven't talked to them
since I said,

353
00:16:00,068 --> 00:16:02,535
"I quit. See you
at the Oscars, bitches."

354
00:16:03,504 --> 00:16:05,638
Come on, let's just
get this over with.

355
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:06,873
