356
00:16:06,875 --> 00:16:08,808
Am I driving you
to the Cheesecake Factory,

357
00:16:08,810 --> 00:16:10,276
or are we having sex?

358
00:16:11,379 --> 00:16:13,680
I'm just... I'm trying
to lighten the mood.

359
00:16:13,682 --> 00:16:15,515
I know. Thank you.
Sorry.

360
00:16:15,517 --> 00:16:17,117
It's just so
humiliating.

361
00:16:17,119 --> 00:16:18,251
So humiliating?

362
00:16:18,253 --> 00:16:20,253
Am I driving you to
the Cheesecake Factory...?

363
00:16:20,255 --> 00:16:22,322
I'm sorry.
I'll-I'll stop. I'll stop.

364
00:16:25,204 --> 00:16:26,671
Come on, don't
look so sad.

365
00:16:26,673 --> 00:16:28,139
You never know
what's gonna happen.

366
00:16:28,141 --> 00:16:30,575
Maybe tonight will be great.
Sweetie, I know you're trying

367
00:16:30,577 --> 00:16:32,911
to make me feel better,
and I love you for that,

368
00:16:32,913 --> 00:16:36,748
but it's making me feel worse,
and I kind of hate you.

369
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:39,517
This isn't your car.

370
00:16:39,519 --> 00:16:42,987
I know. I thought
we'd take yours.

371
00:16:44,323 --> 00:16:46,491
I don't understand.

372
00:16:47,693 --> 00:16:49,994
It's nothing fancy,
but it'll get you to auditions,

373
00:16:49,996 --> 00:16:53,598
and at least for now, you don't
have to go back to waitressing.

374
00:16:55,034 --> 00:16:57,535
I don't know what to say.

375
00:16:57,537 --> 00:17:00,171
Don't say anything.

376
00:17:00,173 --> 00:17:02,240
Oh, my God.

377
00:17:02,242 --> 00:17:04,542
I mean, you could say,
"Thank you."

378
00:17:04,544 --> 00:17:06,644
I did just buy you a car.

379
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:09,948
Mmm.

380
00:17:11,083 --> 00:17:13,251
Look, I admit
that it's odd

381
00:17:13,253 --> 00:17:15,420
that Rajesh didn't
write to you himself,

382
00:17:15,422 --> 00:17:17,188
but if you get to know him,

383
00:17:17,190 --> 00:17:19,457
you'll see
he's just a sweet, regular guy.

384
00:17:19,459 --> 00:17:22,694
As a counterpoint, here he is,
uninvited and visibly sweaty.

385
00:17:22,696 --> 00:17:24,395
Hello, Emily.

386
00:17:24,397 --> 00:17:25,864
Hello.
Amy told me

387
00:17:25,866 --> 00:17:28,900
you were concerned that I might
be too passive and shy.

388
00:17:28,902 --> 00:17:30,602
Let me ask you something.

389
00:17:30,604 --> 00:17:32,737
Would a passive guy
barge in here

390
00:17:32,739 --> 00:17:34,773
