391
00:17:34,775 --> 00:17:38,276
"Hey, dew-kissed flower,
what's up?"

392
00:17:41,981 --> 00:17:45,016
No, but a weird guy
with no boundaries might.

393
00:17:45,018 --> 00:17:46,551
Uh, okay, that's
a separate issue.

394
00:17:46,553 --> 00:17:48,943
Let's put a pin in that and just
focus on the passive thing.

395
00:17:48,944 --> 00:17:50,206
I'm leaving.

396
00:17:50,231 --> 00:17:52,572
Are we still going to go to
that Chaucer reading Friday?

397
00:17:52,959 --> 00:17:55,059
You know, I think
I'm just gonna go by myself.

398
00:17:58,597 --> 00:18:01,132
Not my best first date.

399
00:18:02,368 --> 00:18:04,869
Yeah, but not my worst, either.

400
00:18:09,409 --> 00:18:11,810
