I ever did or said to you!

401
00:18:11,812 --> 00:18:13,678
I'm sorry, too!
It's all my fault!

402
00:18:15,282 --> 00:18:16,481
If you weren't my friend,

403
00:18:16,483 --> 00:18:18,149
